  allLines:
  - speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: cc9e27aaf6abc47b08b7321e23cfc560, type: 2}
    dialogue: Listen closely. I don't have much time.
  - speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: cc9e27aaf6abc47b08b7321e23cfc560, type: 2}
    dialogue: You're the only one who can save Hikaru now.
  - speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 4e1e5cc4d0d394dbbbb193261c90a472, type: 2}
    dialogue: Save? How? Please tell me. I'd do anyting.
  - speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: cc9e27aaf6abc47b08b7321e23cfc560, type: 2}
    dialogue: To bring back the rain, you must appease God Inari.
  - speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: cc9e27aaf6abc47b08b7321e23cfc560, type: 2}
    dialogue: To do so, you need  to collect three offerings.
  - speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: cc9e27aaf6abc47b08b7321e23cfc560, type: 2}
    dialogue: One in the Human Realm, and the other two in the Demi-human realm.
  - speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 4e1e5cc4d0d394dbbbb193261c90a472, type: 2}
    dialogue: Offering? Demi-human Realm? Grandma, I'm confused.
  - speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: cc9e27aaf6abc47b08b7321e23cfc560, type: 2}
    dialogue: Look. You must take the first offering from Landlord Nishijima's castle.
  - speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: cc9e27aaf6abc47b08b7321e23cfc560, type: 2}
    dialogue: Then you must go to the Grand Shrine and enter the Demi-human Realm
      from there to take the rest two.
  - speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 4e1e5cc4d0d394dbbbb193261c90a472, type: 2}
    dialogue: But how do I do that?
  - speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: cc9e27aaf6abc47b08b7321e23cfc560, type: 2}
    dialogue: You'll find out there.
  - speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: cc9e27aaf6abc47b08b7321e23cfc560, type: 2}
    dialogue: Put on my clothes. It'll give you the power to transform to human,
      but only for limited time.
  - speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: cc9e27aaf6abc47b08b7321e23cfc560, type: 2}
    dialogue: This is the only thing I can do for you...
  - speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 4e1e5cc4d0d394dbbbb193261c90a472, type: 2}
    dialogue: I...I got it, grandma.
  - speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: cc9e27aaf6abc47b08b7321e23cfc560, type: 2}
    dialogue: I watched you and Hikaru grew up toghether. How I wish I could spend
      more time with you...
  - speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: cc9e27aaf6abc47b08b7321e23cfc560, type: 2}
    dialogue: This is my last wish...
  - speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 4e1e5cc4d0d394dbbbb193261c90a472, type: 2}
    dialogue: Hikaru is my friend. I'll save him. I swear on my life.
  - speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: cc9e27aaf6abc47b08b7321e23cfc560, type: 2}
    dialogue: Brave child...
